entries.femaleVariant: Nice work in Bolivia. We lost three labs in one night.
You believe Arasaka had a hand in it?
Well, if it were Arasaka, I'd give you my compliments. First-rate sabotage.
Yes, if it were Arasaka... I would thank you for your kind words.
And while we speak of this... Was it you who tried to kidnap Hanako Arasaka?
You are sure? Because if Militech were starting to play rough...
If Militech were starting to play rough, believe me, you'd know.
It's all a lie, an illusion, my dear.
